title: World Of Warcraft - Newcomers From Hell
description:
Newcomers From Hell:

This is an Arena movie, my first of the kind, with a 2v2 team of an Affliction Warlock and Enhancement Shaman.

We are low rating, around 1400-1500, beacuse we do not take it very serious. We play for fun, and to learn. So don&#039;t expect some extreme good pvp or insane tricks.

I frapsed it over a couple of days in the start of Season 3, we have about a 50/50 win ratio.

Hope you enjoy it. :)
